Solomon

I think cookies are definitely suspect for something to be classified as
RESTful at least based on the specific issues raised by Roy Fielding at
http://www.ics.uci.edu/~fielding/pubs/dissertation/evaluation.htm#sec_6_3_4_2.

Having said that I understand where you are coming from in principle. I
would feel comfortable deploying a suggestion as you mentioned as a
practical way to architect an otherwise restful system. Though I am unlikely
to call it fully restful due to the specific issues Roy Fielding refers to
in the section I pointed to.

Dhananjay

